The low-sales regional cluster is materially underperforming versus all other regions across every category. Q1 sales are 60–80% lower than the next weakest region.

Demand profile:

Premium categories: low but present (Premium skincare 300 units; Premium makeup 250 units).
Budget categories: structurally weak and declining (Budget skincare 130; Budget makeup 80).
