Premium skincare: 9 days cover (70 units) – moderate but not growth-supportive.
Budget skincare: 5 days cover (40 units) – frequent stockouts.
Premium makeup: 10 days cover (60 units) – balanced but not expansion-ready.
Budget makeup: 20 days cover (55 units) – high relative to weak demand.
